#Basic Recipe

1.Flour 490g.
2.Boiled Hot Water 280g.
3.Sunflower Oil 2.8 table spoon.
4.Salt 1.4 tea spon.
5.cover the dough and 20min rest

Use 90gram parts of dough for roll out in aproxm 25-27cm radius lavash, in resault after fried should be 22cm lavash

6. Fry for 1 min every side, when fry finished lubricate with water every side of Lavash (use pastry brush or spray) 
